35. [CRITICAL] User requests **test cases** → resolve env + align Phoenix (**Rule PHOENIX-SWITCH.0**; pass env + alignment exit code to subagents; prod `-ConfirmProd` + user ack). Run **cross-dependency-finder** FIRST; pass structured output as `context['cross_dependency_data']` to **test-case-generator**. Never skip cross-dep. **Canonical procedure:** `.cursor/skills/cross-dependency-finder/SKILL.md`, `.cursor/skills/test-case-generator/SKILL.md`. Folder layout: `.cursor/rules/workspace/test_cases_structure.mdc`.

